|------------|----------|---------|--------------------------|
| $max-width | `number` | 100%    | The element width limit. |

## Example

<code-group>

  <code-block label="SCSS" active>

  ```scss
  @use 'more-sass' as more;

  .element {
  	@include more.ellipsis;
  }
