  .element-one {
  	@include more.margin(10px);
  }

  .element-two {
  	@include more.margin(10px 20px 30px 40px); // or: @include more.margin(10px, 20px, 30px, 40px);
  }

  .element-three {
  	@include more.margin(null auto);
  }
  ```

  </code-block>

  <code-block label="Output">

  ```css
  .element-one {
  	margin-top: 10px;
  	margin-right: 10px;
  	margin-bottom: 10px;
  	margin-left: 10px;
  }

  .element-two {
  	margin-top: 10px;
  	margin-right: 20px;
  	margin-bottom: 30px;
  	margin-left: 40px;
  }

  .element-three {
  	margin-right: auto;
  	margin-left: auto;
  }
  ```

  </code-block>

</code-group>

